high_descs: Turn right, walk across the room to the edge of the left counter, then turn left.
Pick up the knife by the kettle.
Turn right, walk across the room, then turn right to face the sink.
Cut the apple on the counter into three pieces.
Turn right, walk across the room until you hit the wall, turn left, and walk until you hit the table.
Place the knife on the table.
Turn right, walk until you hit the wall, then turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the apple slice closest to you.
Turn left, walk to the wall, turn left, and walk till you hit the stove.
Place the apple slice in the back right pot.
Pick up the back right pot with the apple in it.
Turn left, walk until you hit the wall, then turn right to face the table.
Place the pot on the table to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with an apple piece inside it on the table.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter, left of the toaster.
Pick up the knife, on the counter, that is between the bread and toaster.
Turn right, move to the counter left of the sink.
Slice the apple on the counter.
Turn right, move to the table.
Put the knife on the table.
Turn right, move to the counter left of the sink.
Pick up a section of apple from the counter.
Turn right, move to in front of the stove.
Place the apple section into the pan on the right side of the stove.
Pick up the pan, containing the apple section, from the stove.
Turn left, move to the table.
Put the pan on the table, right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan, with an apple section in it, on to the table.

high_descs: Go to the left side of the counter
Pick up the farther knife
Go to the left of the sink
Cut the apple
Go to the white table
Put the knife down on the table
Go to the left of the sink
Pick up an apple piece
Go to the stove
Put the apple on the pot on the right
Pick up the pot
Go to the white table
Put the pot down on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and a pot with an apple slice down on a table
